{"tid":1502941,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我覺得呢條片可以參考下 可以解決畜龍鳩衝嘅問題","createTime":"2019-08-24T18:37:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T19:01:36.000Z","uid":206344,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e8703e92dad045c100b2db59d95b8d395e8d24de","tid":1502941,"uid":206344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T18:37:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HdNn5TZu6R8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHdNn5TZu6R8&d=BZKFieMwLRuYRu3HtqC84uaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=5ca2b6ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HdNn5TZu6R8</a><br />\n2:02<br />\n大家不仿睇下呢條片<br />\n斯巴達盾陣打法好值得我地參考<br />\n全部揸盾同遮一字排開 <br />\n畜龍點都衝唔散我地咁多人<br />\n擋完衝擊再拎遮插<br />\n插完再盾陣擋<br />\n再慢慢退<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最緊要最重要係企前排唔好散陣型<br />\n後面唔好跑走</span></span><br />\n一散就仆街<br />\n<br />\n利申:9up<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf4aeb2c390cfe3434af5399e6ee430788610b1","tid":1502941,"uid":206344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T18:37:36.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"da910eaac3eb4f56b5e3407a710e5f40bab9cb86","tid":1502941,"uid":206344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T18:38:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f41bc2a4d9325a7aac2db6e890866b1db1e104ab","tid":1502941,"uid":206344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T18:38:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84d98145208802260eace2235c18f411b20ceced","tid":1502941,"uid":206344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T18:38:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ab0f5d391965c7c56954789ce5346632e6b5f77","tid":1502941,"uid":206344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T18:38:38.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"1a79f49306694e7cbb3e6e302ea6318a98d2af98","tid":1502941,"